item.title: jhipster'ı kullanmaya başlama
item.description: Windows’ta JHipster Kurulumu # Oracle web sitesinden Java 8’i yükleyin. (İsteğe bağlı) Bir Java oluşturma aracı yükleyin. Whether you choose to use Maven or Gradle, you normally don’t have to install anything, as JHipster will automatically install the Maven Wrapper or the Gradle Wrapper for you. If you don’t want to use those wrappers, go to the official Maven website or Gradle website to do your own installation. Git’i git-scm.com’dan yükleyin.
